    Œªc.Œªn.c(Œªc.Œªn.c(Œªx.x, Œªc.Œªn.n),
    Œªc.Œªn.n))

A Scott value selects the ith of N case-handlers,
applied to its fields:
  Nat Z:    Œªz.Œªs.z
  Nat S(n): Œªn.Œªz.Œªs.s(n)

A Scott nat: Z = Œªs.Œªz.z, S(n) = Œªs.Œªz.s(n).

